## Get all workouts
GET http://localhost:3000/api/workouts

### Get specific workout
GET http://localhost:3000/api/workouts/6a0440d2bd0b9be4c1c02d68

### Create a workout
POST http://localhost:3000/api/workouts
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Push Day",
    "category": "strength",
    "durationMinutes": 75
}

### Create invalid workout
POST http://localhost:3000/api/workouts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "A",
  "category": "strength",
  "durationMinutes": 45
}

### Update workout
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/workouts/6a0440d2bd0b9be4c1c02d68
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Push Day",
  "category": "strength",
  "durationMinutes": 80
}


### Update workout with invalid data
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/workouts/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "A",
  "category": "strength",
  "durationMinutes": 80
}

### Delete workout
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/workouts/6a0440cabd0b9be4c1c02d67


### Delete workout that does not exist
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/workouts/999

